An English Wife! that's a large Latitude, Pud? But I agree to it; Come, Buss, and Friends then!
[Kisses her.]
So now;

I believe, Sir, I have a Guinea of yours— It is too much, to take both your Money and your Mistress; there, Sir;
[Gives him a Guinea]
Now, Sir, I presume your Absence will be very agreeable to this Company.
